h1. Synopsis

	Apache Karaf :: Main

	This bundle is the main Karaf launcher. It's responsible of the Karaf startup including
    the console, branding, etc bootstrap.

	Maven URL:
		[mvn:org.apache.karaf/org.apache.karaf.main/4.0.2]

h1. Description

	This bundle is responsible for the main Karaf startup.

	In particular, it manages the bootstrap of low level Karaf services such as the embedded Derby database, locking
facilities, etc.

